                        <span class="user-stars allstar30 rating" title="还行"></span>
                    <span>2012-08-17</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">小册子见功力，阅读快感不大</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="535357005">
